Rhythmbox MicroBlogger

	Ali Vakilzade <ali.vakilzade [--at--] gmail [--dot--] com>

DESCRIPTION

  A simple plugin to send current music information to a micro blogging service

INSTALL
  1- Remove older version
    (If you have)

  2- install from git or archive
    git is recommended

    from git:
      cd ~/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins/
      git clone git://github.com/aliva/rhythmbox-microblogger.git

    from archive:
      extract downloaded archive to ~/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins/
      you should have __init__.py here
      ~/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins/rhythmbox-microblogger/__init__.py

  3- run/restart Rhythmbox active this plugin and add accounts!

  4- now a button will appear in rhythmbox toolbar. use that for sending notice

LICENSE

